title: External USB 3 display - AOC E1659Fwu review
description:
Today we review the AOC E1659Fwu portable USB 3.0 monitor.

This is a great secondary monitor, that you can throw in your bag, when you need a portable display powered only by USB 3.0.

Check it out on Amazon:
http://amzn.to/2tstFVt

Download the Displaylink driver for Windows, OSX or Android:
http://goo.gl/5FqCGM
